              Our Virgin Deep Wave extensions can be colored, straightened, curled or still worn in their original wave pattern. Our Virgin Deep Wave bundles are never chemically altered and come in a natural black color; however, the wave pattern is machine crafted to uniquely define each wave to ensure its longevity, luxurious texture, and bounce. All bundles are sold separately and weigh approximately 3.5 ounces.
